# Habit Performance Tracker

## Description
This project tracks daily habits and analyzes how they impact performance.
Instead of just tracking streaks, it focuses on understanding whether a habit
actually improves productivity.

## Features
- Add habits
- Log daily performance (1–10 scale)
- Analyze performance trends
- Generate insights based on habit data

## Tech Stack
- Backend: Node.js, Express
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Data Storage: In-memory (for simplicity)

## How It Works
1. User creates a habit.
2. User logs daily performance for that habit.
3. System analyzes data and provides insights.

## API Endpoints
- POST /habits → Create habit
- GET /habits → Get all habits
- POST /log → Add performance log
- GET /insights → View performance insights

